</a> </li>						<li>
<a href="http://freelancewrite.about.com/updated.htm" data-component="categoryList" data-source="CategorySite_All" data-type="item.heading" data-ordinal="18">								Updated Articles and Resources <span class="arrow arrow-right"></span>
</a>						</li>
						<li>
<a href="http://video.about.com/freelancewrite/" data-component="categoryList" data-source="CategorySite_All" data-type="item.heading" data-ordinal="19">								Expert Videos <span class="arrow arrow-right"></span>
</a>						</li>
	</ul>
</div>		                    </div>
		                    <div id="content" class="col col-8">


<article class="list content widget expert-content" itemprop="articleBody">
		<section class="list-unit group">
			<div class="expert-content-text">The following list of 28 freelance writing jobs websites are places that advertise jobs specifically for writers who work remotely or telecommute.</div>
		</section>


		<section class="list-unit group">
		<figure class="content-img content-img-small right-gutter">
			<div class="content-img-wrapper">
<a href="http://beaguide.about.com/" data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articleReview" data-ordinal="1" source="outbound_list"></a><img src="http://f.tqn.com/y/freelancewrite/1/L/V/1/-/-/164383308.jpg" alt="Young woman working from home - Maciej Frolow/Photographer's Choice RF/Getty Images" width="300" height="200" class="" data-pinit-img-url="http://f.tqn.com/y/freelancewrite/1/S/V/1/-/-/164383308.jpg" data-description="28 Places to Find Telecommuting Freelance Writing Jobs: About.com" itemprop="image" >
			
<a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http://freelancewrite.about.com/od/freelancejobresources/tp/Freelance-Jobs.htm?utm_source=pinterest&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=shareurlbuttons_nip&media=http://f.tqn.com/y/freelancewrite/1/S/V/1/-/-/164383308.jpg&description=28 Places to Find Telecommuting Freelance Writing Jobs: About.com" data-component="contentListPage" data-source="pinitBtn" data-type="sharePinterest" data-ordinal="1" data-network="pinterest" title="Pin to Pinterest" class="pinit-btn" data-pin-do="skipLink"></a>			</div>
				<figcaption class="content-img-subtitle">
						<span class="credit pull-right">Maciej Frolow/Photographer's Choice RF/Getty Images</span>
				</figcaption>
		</figure>
				<div class="expert-content-text">
					<h3 class="item-heading">
						<span class="bullet">&bull;</span>
<a href="http://beaguide.about.com/" data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articleReview" data-ordinal="2">								About.com
</a>					</h3>
	
							<p>About.com is always looking for &#34;Guides&#34;- writing experts who work remotely to build quality content in a <a href="/od/manageyourcareer/a/How-To-Research-And-Choose-Your-Freelance-Writing-Niche.htm" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="1">niche</a> site.
								<a href="http://beaguide.about.com/" data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articelReview" data-ordinal="1">More &raquo;</a>
							</p>
				</div>
			</section>

<div id="adsense1" adsense-numlinks="2" adsense-displaylabel="true" class="adsense-slot adsense"></div>
		

		<section class="list-unit group">
				<div class="expert-content-text">
					<h3 class="item-heading">
						<span class="bullet">&bull;</span>
							ACES: American Copy Editor Society
					</h3>
	
							<p>This is a Yahoo group to which you can subscribe. (Search for ACES from the front page of Yahoo Groups to join). I have seen 3-4 freelance/remote positiond come through over the course of a year.
							</p>
				</div>
			</section>

		

		<section class="list-unit group">
				<div class="expert-content-text">
					<h3 class="item-heading">
						<span class="bullet">&bull;</span>
<a href="http://www.asbpe.org/" target="_blank" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articleReview" data-ordinal="3">								American Society of Business Publications Editors
</a>					</h3>
	
							The ASBPE keeps a fair list of jobs for members and non-members alike. Be sure to check the review below for tips!
								<a href="http://www.asbpe.org/" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articelReview" data-ordinal="2">More &raquo;</a>
				</div>
			</section>

<div id="adsense2" adsense-numlinks="2" adsense-displaylabel="true" class="adsense-slot adsense"></div>
		

		<section class="list-unit group">
				<div class="expert-content-text">
					<h3 class="item-heading">
						<span class="bullet">&bull;</span>
<a href="http://www.ap.org/apjobs/index.html" target="_blank" data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articleReview" data-ordinal="4">								Associated Press
</a>					</h3>
	
							The AP website has a job listing page.
								<a href="http://www.ap.org/apjobs/index.html" data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articelReview" data-ordinal="3">More &raquo;</a>
				</div>
			</section>

		

		<section class="list-unit group">
				<div class="expert-content-text">
					<h3 class="item-heading">
						<span class="bullet">&bull;</span>
<a href="http://www.copydesk.net/nf_wrjobs.html" target="_blank" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articleReview" data-ordinal="5">								Copydesk
</a>					</h3>
	
							Copydesk is a freelance placement agency, but samples of their available gigs are shown on this page.
								<a href="http://www.copydesk.net/nf_wrjobs.html" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articelReview" data-ordinal="4">More &raquo;</a>
				</div>
			</section>

<div id="adsense3" adsense-numlinks="1" adsense-displaylabel="true" class="adsense-slot adsense"></div>
		

		<section class="list-unit group">
				<div class="expert-content-text">
					<h3 class="item-heading">
						<span class="bullet">&bull;</span>
<a href="http://www.freelancebbs.com/" target="_blank" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articleReview" data-ordinal="6">								Freelance BBS
</a>					</h3>
	
							<p>Freelance BBS requires a signup/registration, but I haven’t got <a href="http://workingmoms.about.com/od/householdmanagement/a/Stop-Junk-Mail.htm" data-inlink="y3aes3yX6cpym8NqcMy9og&#61;&#61;" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="1">any junk mail</a> (yet) and am happy with the leads.
								<a href="http://www.freelancebbs.com/" target="_blank" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articelReview" data-ordinal="5">More &raquo;</a>
							</p>
				</div>
			</section>

		

		<section class="list-unit group">
				<div class="expert-content-text">
					<h3 class="item-heading">
						<span class="bullet">&bull;</span>
<a href="http://www.freelanceswitch.com" target="_blank" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articleReview" data-ordinal="7">								Freelance Switch
</a>					</h3>
	
							This job board is the only subscription service that I am including in these links, but it’s because I firmly believe in it. For $7 a month, you cut down on the sheer amount of people you are competing against. I got a job from here my very first month, making a 50x ROI over the long run.
								<a href="http://www.freelanceswitch.com" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articelReview" data-ordinal="6">More &raquo;</a>
				</div>
			</section>

		

		<section class="list-unit group">
				<div class="expert-content-text">
					<h3 class="item-heading">
						<span class="bullet">&bull;</span>
<a href="http://www.freelancewritinggigs.com" target="_blank" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articleReview" data-ordinal="8">								Freelance Writing Gigs
</a>					</h3>
	
							Honestly, one of the better job sites out there, its strength lies in the fact that it is so well updated.
								<a href="http://www.freelancewritinggigs.com" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articelReview" data-ordinal="7">More &raquo;</a>
				</div>
			</section>

		

		<section class="list-unit group">
				<div class="expert-content-text">
					<h3 class="item-heading">
						<span class="bullet">&bull;</span>
<a href="http://jobs.magazine.org/search.cfm" target="_blank" data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articleReview" data-ordinal="9">								Magazine Publishers of America
</a>					</h3>
	
							This is a spot that I check weekly.
								<a href="http://jobs.magazine.org/search.cfm" data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articelReview" data-ordinal="8">More &raquo;</a>
				</div>
			</section>

		

		<section class="list-unit group">
				<div class="expert-content-text">
					<h3 class="item-heading">
						<span class="bullet">&bull;</span>
<a href="http://www.mediabistro.com/joblistings/" target="_blank" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articleReview" data-ordinal="10">								Media Bistro
</a>					</h3>
	
							You will have to register, but it is a free service. Once you get the hang of their sorting function, you can find jobs in your area, or choose the telecommute or contractual drop down menu items. Be sure to read the review below for tips on getting the gig.
								<a href="http://www.mediabistro.com/joblistings/" rel=nofollow data-component="contentListPage" data-source="outbound_list" data-type="link.articelReview" data-ordinal="9">More &raquo;</a>
				</div>
			</section>

		
	



